    "Scores are typically visualized using colors (Gat et al., 2022) or bar plots (Kokalj et al., 2021).",
    "Another form is visualization, which includes means such as heatmaps (Jo and Myaeng, 2020), graphs (Vig, 2019), and diagrams (Katz and Belinkov, 2023).",
